  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>Unique and beautifully refurbished boutique-style hotel in Reberty at the top of <a data-udi="umb://document/4eae720ba8984d83a83f530983b4b6f8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4eae720ba8984d83a83f530983b4b6f8}" title="Les Menuires">Les Menuires</a>. We are delighted to introduce Hotel Hillary exclusively to the UK market this winter season, lovingly refurbished by its owner, Mr Van-Heek. With only 17 rooms and situated at 2,000m at the top of Les Menuires in Reberty, the Hotel Hillary has a spectacular setting. The ski-in/ski-out location provides easy access to the excellent pistes of the Three Valleys. Enjoy relaxing in the sauna at the end of the day or make the most of the sunny terrace later in the season. In the evening, the bar offers a cosy place to enjoy a drink, followed by dinner in the excellent restaurant.</span></p>]]></description>
