  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>The 17 bedrooms are all tastefully and comfortably decorated in a modern mountain style</li>
<li>All rooms have 60cm flst screen TV, free Wi-Fi access, tea and coffee making facilities and bathroom with bath or shower and hairdryer</li>
<li>The standard twin/double rooms (A2- specify your preference at time of booking) have a shower and can be taken for sole occupancy (with a supplement)</li>
<li>Superior rooms (C2) have a bath and mountain views</li>
<li>Triple rooms (B3) have either 3 single beds or a double and single bed with bath and mountain view</li>
<li>Family rooms (D4) are on request and have either twin/double bed and bunk beds</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
